properties.name: MathVenture Island CODE COMPLETE
properties.description: Embark on an exciting math journey where you face unique creatures in battles of knowledge. Each "math monster" represents a specific topic, from addition and subtraction to math logic, challenging you with visual and numerical questions. Answer correctly to learn all the creatures, can you defeat them and save the island? With random questions in each game +90 questions stored, the fun and learning never ends with different games every time!
properties.author: Josué Gutiérrez
